longBusinessSummary: EnviroGold Global Limited operates as a clean technology company in Canada. The company focuses on reclaiming mine tailings and resource development waste streams to sell various precious, strategic, and critical metals and metal concentrates. EnviroGold Global Limited is based in Vancouver, Canada.
